title: Sengathu Boomiyile
subTitle: Vallarasu and Chinnasamy are two friends who come from closely related families. However, a fateful incident drives a wedge between them, culminating in a violent fight.

title: Thambikku Entha Ooru
subTitle: Seeing Balu's spendthrift and carefree attitude, his father sends him to his friend's house in a village to get reformed. Things get complicated when he gets entangled in a love triangle.

title: Yeidhavan
subTitle: When Krishna's sister is killed during a college protest, he vows to avenge her. However, he ends up helping the medical students to gain their rights.

title: Sachin
subTitle: A boy is named after Sachin Tendulkar, as his birth coincides with a celebratory day. As he grows older and falls for a woman named Anjali, he finds that they have a lot more in common than usual.

title: Thai Mozhi
subTitle: Rajasimham, a local criminal, falls in love with a woman. However, his wealthy, long-standing enemy, Mariadas, tries his best to disrupt Rajasimham's life.

title: Chidambarathil Oru Appasamy
subTitle: A school teacher leads a carefree life without any goal. However, a pilgrimage to Sabrimalai transforms his life and the lives of his loved ones forever.

title: Shankarlal
subTitle: A criminal, Chelladurai, frames the innocent Dharmalingam for a crime which leads to the latter being jailed. Years later, Dharmalingam returns to take revenge and establish contact with his family.
